1. Initiate collaborative sessions with UI/UX design teams to draft prototypes.
2. Conduct user testing with diverse member groups to ensure proposed changes meet real-world needs.
3. Refine proposals based on recorded feedback and analytical metrics.
4. Implement changes through phased deployments, ensuring continuity and functionality across the platforms.


